0. requires OpenGL and freeglut (http://freeglut.sourceforge.net).
1. cd to directory containing package's source code
2. type ./configure or sh ./configure as appropriate
3. type make
4. cd src
5. type a2b

NOTE: 

1. 'make install' is not supported so please dont use it. To play a2b, start
it from the directory a2b binary is present.

2. Game was tested on nvidia 5200 graphics card.
